{"tid":235212,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"本隊長誠邀15妹出山打救飲食台","createTime":"2017-05-08T22:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T10:08:40.000Z","uid":28031,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc99e31e3678439d436b6513275906335e2f11fc","tid":235212,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T22:27:38.000Z","msg":"今飲食台假膠橫行 癲佬當道，<br />\n歸根究底皆因當年舊登飲食台台柱早已告老還鄉，<br />\n蜀中無大將之時慘遭各大小煩膠小圈子圍爐，<br />\n令當日風光一時嘅飲食台淪為FB之流。<br />\n<br />\n本隊長今為重振飲食台威風，<br />\n隻身冒死來到波台，<br />\n望能找到昔日飲食台猛將之一 - 15妹bb，<br />\n使其重出江湖，一掃飲食台歪風。<br />\n<br />\n如今日15妹bb能助本隊長一臂之力，<br />\n今日所受滴水之恩，他日重振飲食台之時定必當湧泉相報！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n                     好精彩隊長敬上"},{"pid":"9b9f08629bc91cdb94ab1469fc1d35b2f5248b6f","tid":235212,"uid":75805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T22:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804b57457eb9933dfe38bdc6bc72eca440204ebb","tid":235212,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T22:34:31.000Z","msg":"死返高登啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64accdd94ea11ba4c7b81fe756e0bb6f3a777958","tid":235212,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:28:13.000Z","msg":"猶記得當年15妹bb所炮製嘅各種海鮮菜餚，<br />\n配以劃時代嘅心心圖案點綴，<br />\n令人隔住螢光幕都可以感受到色香味鮮，<br />\n已經足以證明15妹bb係飲食台中無人能出其右嘅海鮮高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b683b97eeb6042398f65dab8586fb48e84c075f","tid":235212,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:30:54.000Z","msg":"要數當中不得不提嘅經典中嘅經典<br />\n肯定係15妹bb為老公"},{"pid":"ddbae0970ca45878a25d53a6e65bae4f07c54c04","tid":235212,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T23:34:38.000Z","msg":"要數當中不得不提嘅經典中嘅經典<br />\n肯定係15妹bb為老公所準備嘅<br />\n公仔麵(數條）湯飯飯盒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 能夠將白飯同公仔麵（幾條）完美結合，<br />\n更將飯盒料理昇華到另一個前所未有嘅新境界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ab152a614e3e694732c2fcde9653d018c4cff2","tid":235212,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T05:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e391be4765593b117b4d40e7a14030d8fe80f5d","tid":235212,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T05:57:44.000Z","msg":"呢位ching中二病發❓"},{"pid":"5d4daee21652ba5eac07ca24c67a49b748552f9a","tid":235212,"uid":37798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T05:58:33.000Z","msg":"死返巴狗啦"},{"pid":"64f59938c461d36824d00c1af0590db60d3bb62c","tid":235212,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢位ching中二病發❓</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔是呀"},{"pid":"d93b7880d40d79b0a4e974fd85dd2786b1282a5d","tid":235212,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 15妹起左身⼀⼀⼁⼃"},{"pid":"06473ebee126d618bfcb9701713b2761d5bdccf6","tid":235212,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ag0Rgj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ag0Rgj.jpg&h=19c6552a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w2Qp1hT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2Qp1hT.jpg&h=5523862f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵唔到其他圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676581fcdc3413b26a3a739465654c4c3f513d3b","tid":235212,"uid":13732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\